@startuml geometric
skinparam linetype ortho

title Geometric Routing & The Wavefront Search

state "Current State: Chord(C)" as C
state "Projected Rotation (Targeting 'A')" as ProjA
state "Next State: Chord(A)" as ChordA
state "Projected Rotation (Targeting 'T')" as ProjT
state "LSM Stored Paths (Neighborhood of C)" as LSM {
  state "Path: C -> A" as PathA
  state "Path: C -> O" as PathO
  state "Path: C -> U" as PathU
  
  note right of PathA
    <b>Constructive Interference</b>
    XOR reveals high resonance/saturation.
    Math aligns perfectly with projection.
  end note
  
  note right of PathO
    <b>Destructive Interference</b>
    XOR reveals noise/high entropy.
    Path is pruned.
  end note
}

C -> ProjA : Apply Momentum/Rotation
ProjA --> LSM : XOR against physical memory

PathA --> ChordA : Move &amp; Update Phase
ChordA -> ProjT : Continue Braid...

@enduml